title: Going Over A Twitter Exchange With A Moral Realist
description:
In this video I review a recent Twitter exchange I had with a moral realist.

Note: At one point I say that moral relativists would agree that moral codes are on the same footing with respect to objective truth. Typically relativist views relativize the moral facts to stances, and these are the sorts of views I was talking about when I said that. However, theoretically a moral relativist can relativize the moral facts to something stance-independent.

Article I mentioned: 

https://www.lanceindependent.com/p/to-wake-up-as-a-villain?utm_source=profile&utm_medium=reader2

description:
